Subject: Re: [T2] Starting/oil question

If you have hydraulic lifters you will get a few seconds rattle.  The 
pressure light switch is a different matter.  Are you sure it is really 
taking that long.  Mine with the sender i am currently using because of 
its location takes about 1.5 seconds to register.
jimt
